To plot this data as a scatter plot, with length on the x axis and weight on the y axis, we would do this:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(my_dataframe, aes(x = length, y = weight)) +
  geom_point()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](02-03_visualisation_files/figure-html/fruit_scatter-1.png){width=672}
:::
